node.text: Drumoll, please! 🥁 We’re thrilled to announce the inaugural recipients of the 2021 REAL Change Scholarship for Social Justice. These 15  @americaneagle and @aerie associates from across the U.S. are actively driving anti-racism, equality and social justice initiatives in their communities and are demonstrating the power of their actions and voices to make REAL change! Check out stories to learn more about a few of the recipients and their platforms. Give them a big 👏 below! Congratulations!
